==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ultrazodiacal
<hw>Ul`tra*zo*di"a*cal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>ultra-</ets> + <ets> zodiacal</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Astron.)</fld>
<def>Outside the zodiac; being in that part of the heavens that is more
than eight degrees from the ecliptic; <as>as, <ex>ultrazodiacal</ex>
planets, that is, those planets which in part of their orbits go beyond
the zodiac</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ultroneous</ent>⟦br⟧
